1/Let's start the week off with a #COVID19 #vaccine update. Last week, our state administered 125,176 doses.  

70,509 were final doses. That's 70K people who, in 2 weeks, will be fully vaccinated. 

Put differently, 5.25% of the entire *state* got vaccinated last week. https://t.co/RlWFCO4nhC
